short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly switch current tab or link from incognito window to normal window, or vice versa.
short.zh_CN: 快速切换页面，链接，文字搜索的隐身或正常模式。
short.zh_TW: 快速切換分頁，網頁連結，文字搜尋的無痕或一般模式。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension enables you to switch incognito mode of current tab or link with one click, so you can switch current session easily.
